OL,4,Cripping off customers
OL,6,FA rogue roofer has been jailed for six
OL,7,Fyears after deliberately ripping off
OL,8,Fhis customers with overpriced repairs.
OL,10,FTerry Green, 27, gained his victims'
OL,11,Ftrust by initially charging reasonable
OL,12,Fprices before telling them additional
OL,13,Fand far more expensive work was needed.
OL,15,FIn June 2022, Green revisited the home
OL,16,Fof an elderly couple in Sandwich who
OL,17,Fhe had previously carried out work
OL,18,Ffor, to ask if they wanted him to
OL,19,Frepair their damaged chimney.
