OL,3,CRoofer jailed for six years for
OL,4,Cripping off customers
OL,6,FHe initially quoted #350 but later
OL,7,Ftold them their entire roof needed
OL,8,Freplacing at a cost of #20,000,
OL,9,Feventually settling on an agreed price
OL,10,Fof around #7,000.
OL,12,FThe couple ended up paying a total of
OL,13,F#3,090 before their bank grew
OL,14,Fsuspicious and stopped any further
OL,15,Ftransactions.
OL,17,FKent Police became aware of his
OL,18,Foffending two months earlier when a
OL,19,Fresident of Westgate, Thanet, reported
OL,20,Fpaying him #1,650 for repairs that
OL,21,Fwere then not completed.
