OL,3,CRoofer jailed for six years for
OL,4,Cripping off customers
OL,6,FThe woman told officers she had agreed
OL,7,Fto the work after originally being
OL,8,Fquoted #45 to replace a roof tile, and
OL,9,Fthen transferred the additional larger
OL,10,Fsum as a deposit for further repairs.
OL,12,FHowever, Green packed up his tools and
OL,13,Fleft the property after she
OL,14,Freconsidered and insisted on obtaining
OL,15,Fa second opinion.
OL,17,FGreen, of Iver, Buckinghamshire, was
OL,18,Farrested in Minster, Thanet, on Monday
OL,19,F13 June 2022 and later charged with
OL,20,Ftwo counts of fraud.
