OL,3,CRoofer jailed for six years for
OL,4,Cripping off customers
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Adam Stallard of
OL,7,Fthe Kent and Essex Serious Crime
OL,8,FDirectorate said, "Terry Green could
OL,9,Fhave earned an honest living as a
OL,10,Froofer but made a conscious decision
OL,11,Fto cheat his customers out of their
OL,12,Fhard-earned money."
OL,14,F"Such criminals cause great financial
OL,15,Fhardship to those they trick into
OL,16,Fpaying over the odds for substandard
OL,17,Fwork, as well as a loss of confidence
OL,18,Fin the many honest tradespeople who
OL,19,Fwork hard every day."
