OL,3,CRoofer jailed for six years for
OL,4,Cripping off customers
OL,6,F"Green cold-called at his victims'
OL,7,Fhomes to tell them their property was
OL,8,Fin need of repair. I would strongly
OL,9,Fadvise anyone who receives a similar
OL,10,Fknock at their door to carefully
OL,11,Fconsider their options before agreeing
OL,12,Fto any work, and to always seek a
OL,13,Fsecond opinion first."
